(28, 'Do You Know Me', 'Thriller,', 'Una joven recién graduada descubre que podría no ser quien cree.', '936', 2009, '2020-10-24T22:35Z', '2020-10-25T00:10Z', '95', 'MV002513980000', '197979', '2009-02-19', 'en', 'Ellie encuentra en un cartón de leche la foto de una niña perdida hace años, a la que se asemeja bastante. En broma, llama al número del anuncio, pero pronto se da cuenta que podría tratarse de ella. Cuanto más averigua, más peligroso se vuelve todo.', '109111'),
(29, 'QTH', 'Drama,War,', 'Un suboficial, un cabo y dos marinos tienen que controlar la entrada estratégica de un canal.', '984', 2016, '2020-10-24T22:40Z', '2020-10-25T00:25Z', '105', 'MV010734610000', '14991880', '2016', 'es', 'En el Canal Beagle, un suboficial, un cabo y dos marinos tienen la misión de cuidar y controlar la entrada estratégica del canal. Ellos viven una experiencia de guerra con la amenaza de invasión inglesa hasta llegar a una situación extrema.', '79680'),
(30, 'Peppermint', 'Action,Thriller,', 'A woman seeks vigilante justice against the thugs who attacked and killed her husband and daughter.', '553', 2018, '2020-10-24T22:45Z', '2020-10-25T00:30Z', '105', 'MV011009000000', '15320759', '2018-09-07', 'en', 'Riley North awakens from a coma after surviving a brutal attack that killed her husband and daughter. When the system shields the murderers from justice, Riley sets out to transform herself from citizen to urban guerrilla. Channeling frustration into motivation, the young widow spends years in hiding -- honing her mind, body and spirit to become an unstoppable force. Eluding the underworld, the police and the FBI, Riley embarks on a deadly quest to deliver her own personal brand of justice.', '16153'),
(31, 'The Crow', 'Action,Fantasy,', 'A bird leads a resurrected musician (Brandon Lee) to his killers.', '540', 1994, '2020-10-24T22:45Z', '2020-10-25T00:30Z', '105', 'MV000379160000', '15206', '1994-05-11', 'en', 'The night before his wedding, musician Eric Draven (Brandon Lee) and his fiancée are brutally murdered by members of a violent inner-city gang. On the anniversary of their death, Eric rises from the grave and assumes the gothic mantle of the Crow, a supernatural avenger. Tracking down the thugs responsible for the crimes and mercilessly murdering them, Eric eventually confronts head gangster Top Dollar (Michael Wincott) to complete his macabre mission.', '16620'),
(32, 'The Addams Family', 'Comedy,', 'Gomez, Morticia and their ghoulish household are prey to a scam involving long-lost Uncle Fester.', '037', 1991, '2020-10-24T22:50Z', '2020-10-25T00:55Z', '125', 'MV000342250000', '13571', '1991-11-22', 'en', 'When a man (Christopher Lloyd) claiming to be Fester, the missing brother of Gomez Addams (Raul Julia), arrives at the Addams\' home, the family is thrilled. However, Morticia (Anjelica Huston) begins to suspect the man is a fraud, since he cannot recall details of Fester\'s life. With the help of lawyer Tully Alford (Dan Hedaya), Fester manages to get the Addams clan evicted from their home. Gomez realizes the two men are conspiring to swindle the Addams fortune and that he must challenge Fester.', '10093'),
