(103, 'I.Q.', 'Romantic comedy,', 'Einstein (Walter Matthau) plays matchmaker for niece (Meg Ryan) and mechanic (Tim Robbins).', '586', 1994, '2020-10-25T00:00Z', '2020-10-25T01:38Z', '98', 'MV000411520000', '16301', '1994', 'en', 'Catherine Boyd (Meg Ryan) is a highly intelligent doctoral student at Princeton University and is engaged to stuffy Professor James Moreland (Stephen Fry). Ed Walters (Tim Robbins), a mechanic and all-around regular guy, falls for Catherine and searches for a way to impress her. Believing that the key to Catherine\'s heart is his IQ, Ed passes himself off as a physicist with the help of Catherine\'s uncle, who just happens to be Albert Einstein (Walter Matthau).', '34901'),
