(173, 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2', 'Science fiction,Adventure,Action,Fantasy,Comedy,', 'The team unravels the mystery of Peter Quill\'s true parentage in the outer reaches of the galaxy.', '058', 2017, '2020-10-25T01:00Z', '2020-10-25T04:00Z', '180', 'MV007508410000', '11714883', '2017-05-05', 'en', 'Peter Quill and his fellow Guardians are hired by a powerful alien race, the Sovereign, to protect their precious batteries from invaders. When it is discovered that Rocket has stolen the items they were sent to guard, the Sovereign dispatch their armada to search for vengeance. As the Guardians try to escape, the mystery of Peter\'s parentage is revealed.', '11097'),
