(181, 'Rocky III', 'Drama,', 'Ex-champ boxer (Sylvester Stallone) trains for rematch with new champ (Mr. T).', '625', 1982, '2020-10-25T01:00Z', '2020-10-25T03:30Z', '150', 'MV000100080000', '5610', '1982-05-28', 'en', 'Having become the world heavyweight champion, former working-class boxer Rocky Balboa (Sylvester Stallone) is rich and famous beyond his wildest dreams, which has made him lazy and overconfident. In a double whammy, he loses his trainer and father figure Mickey (Burgess Meredith) and then has his title stolen by the arrogant, menacing challenger Clubber Lang (Mr. T). Turning to his former adversary, Apollo Creed (Carl Weathers), for help, Rocky struggles to get his old fire back.', '16108'),
(182, 'Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark', 'Horror,Thriller,', 'Terrifying tales become all too real for a group of teens who stumble upon a girl\'s spooky home.', '557', 2019, '2020-10-25T01:00Z', '2020-10-25T03:00Z', '120', 'MV012189030000', '16357092', '2019-08-09', 'en', 'The shadow of the Bellows family has loomed large in the small town of Mill Valley for generations. It\'s in a mansion that young Sarah Bellows turns her tortured life and horrible secrets into a series of scary stories. These terrifying tales soon have a way of becoming all too real for a group of unsuspecting teens who stumble upon Sarah\'s spooky home.', '25272'),
(183, 'Kamikaze', 'Action,Comedy drama,', 'Los planes de suicidio de Slatan cambian cuando su vuelo de Moscú a Madrid es cancelado.', '982', 2014, '2020-10-25T01:00Z', '2020-10-25T02:33Z', '93', 'MV008532370000', '11558477', '2014', 'es-ES', 'Los planes de suicidio de Slatan, un hombre corriente de Karadjistan movido por el dolor, cambian cuando su vuelo de Moscú a Madrid es cancelado debido a una tormenta de nieve y todos los pasajeros son realojados en un hotel de montaña.', '52208'),
