(351, 'Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom', 'Adventure,Action,', 'Jones (Harrison Ford), a singer (Kate Capshaw) and an orphan (Ke Huy Quan) look for missing stones.', '069', 1984, '2020-10-25T03:40Z', '2020-10-25T06:00Z', '140', 'MV000213140000', '9614', '1984-05-23', 'en', 'The second of the Lucas/Spielberg Indiana Jones epics is set a year or so before the events in Raiders of the Lost Ark. Indy needs to retrieve a precious gem and several kidnapped young boys on behalf of a remote East Indian village. This time he teams up with a night club singer and a 12-year old boy.', '11163'),
